data.text:
A family tree icon after the sex icon shows the person has a known DNA match to the Jefferies family confirmed by records.

A DNA spiral icon after the sex icon shows the person took a DNA test or has a living descendant tested.

This site is an ongoing work and so does contain errors and omissions. Additions, corrections and comments are welcome. Click on my name below to send an email, please add the person's reference number (#341 for example) found under their name.

If you use the information herein for your own research make sure you verify it first. A link to this site would be appreciated if you use the data from this site.
